.TH "nvme_init_get_log_cmd_effects" 9 "nvme_init_get_log_cmd_effects" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_get_log_cmd_effects \- Initialize passthru command for Commands Supported and Effects
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_get_log_cmd_effects
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "enum nvme_csi csi "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_cmd_effects_log *effects_log "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Passthru command to use
.IP "csi" 12
Command Set Identifier
.IP "effects_log" 12
User address to store the effects log
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Get Log command with
LID value NVME_LOG_LID_CMD_EFFECTS.
